<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Björn Orri Guðmundsson — CEO &amp; Founder, Aftra</title>
    <meta name="description" content="CEO & Founder of Aftra. Building technology that helps executives understand their cybersecurity posture from a hacker's perspective." />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Björn Orri Guðmundsson" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="CEO & Founder of Aftra. Building technology that helps executives understand their cybersecurity posture from a hacker's perspective." />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://lettfeti.com" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Roboto+Slab:wght@400;700&display=swap" />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      :root {
        --color-bg: #F8F8FA;
        --color-text: #18181E;
        --color-muted: #3F3D56;
        --color-accent: #5A4DDE;
        --color-accent-hover: #342B99;
        --color-border: #E2E2E9;
        --font-body: 'Poppins', system-ui, sans-serif;
        --font-display: 'Roboto Slab', Georgia, serif;
      }
      html {
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-family: var(--font-body);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      body { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
      main { width: 100%; max-width: 640px; padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
      header { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1.25rem; }
      .photo { width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 3px solid var(--color-border); }
      h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; color: var(--color-text); }
      .title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: -0.5rem; }
      .title a { color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
      .title a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
      .bio p { font-size: 1.0625rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.75; }
      .bio a { color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
      .bio a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
      .cta a { display: inline-block; background: var(--color-accent); color: #fff; font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 500; padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; }
      .cta a:hover { background: var(--color-accent-hover); }
      footer { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; padding-top: 0.5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
      footer a { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; }
      footer a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
      footer svg { fill: currentColor; flex-shrink: 0; }
      @media (max-width: 768px) { main { padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem; gap: 1.75rem; } h1 { font-size: 1.875rem; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <header>
        <img src="/photo.jpg" alt="Björn Orri Guðmundsson" class="photo" width="120" height="120" />
        <div>
          <h1>Björn Orri Guðmundsson</h1>
          <p class="title">CEO &amp; Founder, <a href="https://aftra.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Aftra</a></p>
        </div>
      </header>
      <section class="bio">
        <p>I'm a founder and engineer obsessed with turning security complexity into business clarity. At <a href="https://aftra.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Aftra</a>, I'm building technology that gives executives a live, data-driven understanding of how their organizations look from a hacker's perspective — transforming cybersecurity from an inconvenient fear into a strategic advantage.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="cta">
